Activity 1: Create an Approval Process for High-Discount Student Enrollment

Note: Before implementing the Approval Process, ensure that the following milestones are completed: Profiles creation (Admin, Counselor, Manager) ; Roles hierarchy setup ; Users creation and role assignment 
This approval process ensures that student enrollments with high discounts are reviewed and approved by a manager, preventing revenue loss and enforcing business policies. 

Create Classic Email Template 
This email template will notify the approver when a high-discount enrollment is submitted for approval. 
Steps to Create Email Template Go to Setup (gear icon on top-right): 
    1. In the Quick Find box, type Email Templates
    2. Click on Classic Email Templates
    3. Click New Template

